Package farm.game

This package implements all of the game logic required for the farm simulator
Version:
1.0
Author:
Lewis Marshall and Megan Steenkamp
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FarmItem
    This interface declares the functions that must be implemented by all Farm Items (Animals, Crops, Items).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AfricanFarm
    This class represents a type of Farm in Africa.
    Animal
    This class implements the base class for all animals.
    Avocado
    The abstract class implementing an Avocado crop.
    Chicken
    This class implements a Chicken, which is a subclass of Animal.
    Coffee
    Implements a crop of type Coffee.
    Compost
    Implements Compost.
    Cotton
    Implements a crop of type Cotton.
    Crop
    The class implementing the base class for all crops.
    Farm
    This class implements the base class for all farms.
    Farmer
    This class implements a farmer, the user's character.
    Fertilizer
    Implements Fertilizer.
    GameEnvironment
    This abstract class implements the game environment which contains all of the game logic.
    GeneralStore
    This class implements the General Store, where various farming items can be viewed and purchased.
    Grain
    Implements a crop of type Grain.
    Hoe
    Implements a Hoe item.
    Horse
    This class implements a Horse, which is a subclass of Animal.
    Item
    The class implementing the base class for all items.
    MediterraneanFarm
    This class represents a type of Farm in the Mediterranean.
    NewZealandFarm
    This class represents a type of Farm in New Zealand.
    NorthKoreanFarm
    This class represents a type of farm in North Korea.
    Olive
    Instantiates a crop of type Olive.
    Pig
    This class instantiates a Pig.
    Rice
    Instantiates a crop of type Rice.
    Silage
    Implements a Silage item.
    Steroid
    Implements Steroids.
    Wheat
    Instantiates a crop of type Wheat.
